{"tid":241342,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「有圖」之關你卵事","createTime":"2017-05-13T05:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T06:09:23.000Z","uid":68676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccdc50bbd2cfd14096e4397103ce0019019eae62","tid":241342,"uid":68676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:55:54.000Z","msg":"呢d咩昆蟲既蛋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以前已經見過1次 冇為意就丟佐 點知今日番工起身搵褲就發現佐又有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  跟手又丟佐佢 跟住叫我屋企人睇下其他衫褲會唔會有 點知又真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n有冇高手知道呢個係乜卵野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n安已不<br />\n仲有d印起度 <br />\n好撚識生 頭2次都係起塞頭哥個位生蛋 <br />\n依家唸起都打冷震 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864e003a69c893931700317cf2e21ff9371ee3cb","tid":241342,"uid":4816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:56:22.000Z","msg":"臭屁蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a55923f8dcc788f2ee740c8190d4ada79384b2e0","tid":241342,"uid":66604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:56:47.000Z","msg":"臭屁蟲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9f8ae763b618dff75d96933e2db47b5add36f7","tid":241342,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪㗎 有冇巴打試過"},{"pid":"3af32c14b862bbe4a4541508846bf3612363e8a9","tid":241342,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"一生就係14粒 好撚嘔心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16eda0baabb82359efaf97eee0185bca5a30114","tid":241342,"uid":68676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e683af2990f469431f6f714d1e2e757be21f56f1","tid":241342,"uid":59414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:00:47.000Z","msg":"陳澤森指，臭屁蟲雖然氣味刺鼻，但不算害蟲，亦不會傳播傳染病，市區內數量增加可能與市區綠化計劃有關，屋邨多了植物，因此在新界區逐漸變得更為常見。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，臭味是臭屁蟲的防禦機制之一，另外臭屁蟲的成蟲或蟲卵感到危險時，亦會分泌出具刺激性的針液，同樣惡臭難聞，接觸皮膚時可能導致敏感甚至損傷。<br />\n<br />\n他建議，如市民發現其蹤影，可用硬卡紙將其掃走，又或用毛巾包裹好，小心將蟲或卵拿走，切勿把它們弄穿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1769217/%E8%87%AD%E5%B1%81%E8%9F%B2%E7%A0%B4%E8%9B%8B%E8%80%8C%E5%87%BA%E3%80%80%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%BB%85%E8%9F%B2%E7%A7%98%E6%8A%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1769217%2F%25E8%2587%25AD%25E5%25B1%2581%25E8%259F%25B2%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E8%259B%258B%25E8%2580%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%25BB%2585%25E8%259F%25B2%25E7%25A7%2598%25E6%258A%2580&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=83b29a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1769217/%E8%87%AD%E5%B1%81%E8%9F%B2%E7%A0%B4%E8%9B%8B%E8%80%8C%E5%87%BA%E3%80%80%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%95%99%E4%BD%A0%E6%BB%85%E8%9F%B2%E7%A7%98%E6%8A%80</a>"},{"pid":"d518b149e88beb92fdea77cf2661084ffe23b8c8","tid":241342,"uid":24961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T06:00:57.000Z","msg":"臭屁蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"